snippet.title: Ovine Replica — Music Preview
snippet.description:
A sample of music composed by Strung and Matthew L. as featured in the first visual novel from independent game studio Amorous Ursidae. Between turmoil and tranquility, Ovine Replica: Serenity in Flesh is a tale of facing heartbreak and finding fulfillment in a sundered city.

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/search/?publisher=Amorous%20Ursidae
itch.io: https://amorous-ursidae.itch.io/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/vrsvsamori
